<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:302px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Government-Vedder-Highsmith-detail-1.jpeg" class="image" title="Detail from Elihu Vedder, Government (1896). Library of Congress Thomas Jefferson Building, Washington, D.C."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cd/Government-Vedder-Highsmith-detail-1.jpeg/300px-Government-Vedder-Highsmith-detail-1.jpeg" width="300" height="190" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
